<br>
Not so sure how good the spell shield is but most of the AoE's in the planes I have encountered have been 30secs at the shortest...  Emp robe would get ya back 25 hps over that time vs the 40 the spell shield should negate.  But I gotta agree with you the 5hps regen over the long haul would be better for longer AoE intervals and raiding in general plus soloing.  Does anyone know if multiple spellshield mods stack?<br>
<br>
A crit mod would be worthwhile as well if they could code it.  Something in the order of 3-7% seems about right...<br>
<br>
What about a flappy mod?  They can make mage focus items for pets, why not have a flappy mod on the robe that buffs all flappys when he is created that boosts the stats he lends to a wizzard...<br>
<br>
How about a right click Old School manaburn with a longer than usual reuse time?  Would a longer reuse time help balance out the power it would grant its wearer?  <br>
<br>
Hrm...  How about a right click Short time DA?  ~12 secs.  Long resuse timer.  Not like you have alot of time in the elementals to click it on boss mobs but still usefull if you have uber assist heal clerics and fast reflexes...<br>
<br>
How about a 10 tick, right click crit booster... Say +25-50% frequency, long reuse time... &quot;Rage of Solusek&quot;  Kinda akin to a Ranger Trueshot ability...<br>
<br>
Just some ideas to float out there...<br>
